body:
## 🐛 Bug Report

 The border property is lost when duplicate a WS and merge cells 

Lib version: 4.2.1

## Steps To Reproduce

<!-- The exact steps required to reproduce the issue, ideally with a code example -->

```javascript
async function readData () {
    const workbook = new Excel.Workbook();
    await workbook.xlsx.readFile('MODELLO.xlsx');
    const ws1 = workbook.getWorksheet('1')
    let copySheet = workbook.addWorksheet("2")
    
    copySheet.model = Object.assign(ws1.model, {
        mergeCells: ws1.model.merges
    })

    copySheet.name = "2"
    console.log(ws1.getCell('G44').style)
    console.log(copySheet.getCell('G44').style)
    
    await workbook.xlsx.writeFile('MODELLO_PROVA.xlsx', {
        useStyles: true
    });
}
```
Result:
```
